 {"title": "Deliverability risks from high-volume AI sends", "detail": "Autonomous email agents sending hundreds of personalized emails daily can trigger spam filters and damage domain reputation if not carefully managed. 11x includes deliverability infrastructure, but the risk is higher than human-paced sending. Domain warm-up and monitoring are critical, and teams have reported deliverability issues during initial ramp-up."},
 {"title": "Category is too new for proven ROI benchmarks", "detail": "AI SDRs emerged in 2023-2024. There's no five-year track record of consistent performance data. Case studies exist, but most come from the vendor or early adopters with favorable conditions. Buying 11x today requires a willingness to experiment, not just deploy."},
